  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study introduce cases of simultaneous multiple cruciate ligament reconstructions with a
      single free tendon Achilles allograft using new technique.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
  <start_date>May 2011</start_date>
